These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, japanese
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the japanese is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | japanese    | canadian |
| Sport         | volleyball | lacrosse    |
| Transport     | skateboard     | helicopter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, dutch
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the colombian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | coffee  | tea   |
| Nationality   | dutch | colombian  |
| Transport     | scooter   | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, cooking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, epic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | traveling   | cooking  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | disaster  |
| Sport         | rowing   | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, potato
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, zombie
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, trike
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | zucchini | potato |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | spy   |
| Transport     | trike       | roller      |

