.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, mango
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the project-manager##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | mango | nectarine     |
| Job     | social-worker | project-manager |
| Sport   | weightlifting | rowing    |

 #################################

 
