.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, corn
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, skydiving
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | corn | plum  |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku |
| Pet     | hedgehog  | chinchilla     |

