.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, singing
There are 2 different nationalities: british, japanese
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the british is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | singing | chess |
| Nationality   | british     | japanese     |
| Pet           | fish          | guinea-pig     |

